@Johnny Depp My heart goes out to you because I know your heart is hurting.   It is so hard not to love beauty.  Sadly, I have seen very young pretty girls in classrooms being adored by everyone.  Even other girls try to get their attention constantly so they can have the envy of other girls and boys that the girl even talks to them. Even the teachers will favor beautiful children and give them sweeter attention.  It’s terrible, because the girls become numb, uncaring, and spoiled by being in everyone’s eyes as so special,  they don’t have to learn to love back, or give anything, or feel for others because it is all coming their way, constantly.  Even adults will comment on how beautiful a child is to her parents, in front of her.  It ruins their hearts.  They haven’t felt rejection or hurt and can’t emphasize with anyone, and if things don’t go their way, they will invent issues to have extra attention through sympathy.  Their looks will bring them everything they want.   It’s a sad thing because their hearts grow hollow.
Have you noticed how this beautiful woman you love rolls her eyes a lot, lol.  It’s only partial, but almost constant.  Like nothing is ever good enough.  It’s almost as if even when she’s in the limelight, she is rather bored with it all.    Beauty is just a robber, a thief of goodness of the heart, and people who love this beauty will probably suffer eventually, as they are cast aside like a toy that is not longer what the adored one wants...she wants something new so she can feel something again...something that she doesn’t even understand.  She can’t give back, because she doesn’t know how to love anyone by herself.  
You are talented and handsome and loved by so may admiring fans.  You can have anyone you want.  When you find a lovely lady that isn’t so self-centered, you will have all the joy again.  You might always have a little pang of pain from what has hurt you, but you will have your pride back..........remember that this beautiful woman never really learned to love someone like you know how to love.  She cannot love deeply.          
🌸Keep smiling cuz your fans smile with you when you do!
